# DeepFang v0.2.0

**Goliath Execution Isolation Stack** — three-stage sanitize → adjudicate → dispatch pipeline with hard Docker network isolation. Integrates with robofang, openclaude-mcp, and openmanus-mcp as a trusted execution sandbox.

[![Status: Active](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Active-green.svg)](README.md)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![FastMCP](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastMCP-3.2.4-orange.svg)](https://github.com/jlowin/fastmcp)

> v0.1.0 was generated by DeepSeek V4 Pro with fictional container references. v0.2.0 replaces them with custom implementations. See [docs/SALVAGE_PLAN.md](docs/SALVAGE_PLAN.md) for the full history.

---

## Architecture

```
User / MCP Client / RoboFang / openclaude-mcp / openmanus-mcp
        │
        ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   Supervisor          │  FastAPI + FastMCP 3.2 SSE
│   Ports 10956/10957  │  React dashboard (10957)
└──────────┬───────────┘
           │
           ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   Sanitizer Shim      │  Custom Python/FastAPI (~220 lines)
│   Port 10958          │  Regex rules → threat scoring → optional Ollama
│                       │  POST /sanitize → {allowed, threat_score, reason}
└──────────┬────────────┘
           │ allowed
           ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   DeepSeek Bridge     │  Custom Python/FastAPI (complete)
│   Port 10959          │  Proxies to DeepSeek cloud API
│                       │  POST /adjudicate → {verdict, rationale}
└──────────┬────────────┘
           │ approve only
           ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   Worker              │  Custom Python/FastAPI (~280 lines)
│   Port 10960          │  Air-gapped (Docker internal: true, no WAN)
│                       │  Allowlist enforcement, command + task modes
│                       │  POST /execute → {success, output, exit_code}
└──────────────────────┘
```

### Network Isolation

| Network | WAN | Services |
|---------|-----|----------|
| `deepfang-sanitize` | No | Sanitizer, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-adjudicate` | Yes | DeepSeek Bridge, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-worker` | **No (`internal: true`)** | Worker, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-internal` | No | Prometheus, Loki, Promtail, Grafana |

Worker WAN isolation is enforced at the **Docker network layer**, not in software.

