## Quick Start

```powershell
git clone https://github.com/sandraschi/deepfang
cd deepfang
copy .env.example .env   # set DEEPSEEK_API_KEY
.\start.ps1              # naked-PC compliant — installs docker/node if missing
```

Dashboard opens automatically at `http://localhost:10957`.

